WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:18.000
Hey, yeah, I wanna shoot, baby, shoot, shoot, shoot, shoot, shoot, shoot, shoot, shoot, ba-do-ba-do-ba-do. Packed in your stash, sassy in the back, bruh, I wanna thank your mother for a butt like that. Gimme some fries with the Shake Shack, baby, if Looks could kill you, would be a Louisiana shotgun.

00:00:18.000 --> 00:00:38.000
Bang! Wha- Oh, oh, hello. I know, right? Whose balls did I have to fondle to get my very own movie? I can't tell you, but it does rhyme with pulverine. And let me tell you, he's got a nice pair of smooth criminals down under.

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:51.000
Anyway, I got places to be, a face to fix, and, oh, bad guys to kill. ♪♪ Maximum effort. ♪♪